<item>
            <title>[LU-19873] Fix issues with Lustre headers</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19873</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre headers suffer from a few problems:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Not using search paths correctly i.e. &quot;&quot; vs &amp;lt;&amp;gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Globally scoped headers for internal interfaces&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Strange dependencies between headers&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Not including-what-you-use&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Headers can&apos;t compile stand alone&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;uapi header compilation test is part of sanity.sh rather than the build system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;All this and more - will be addressed as part of this ticket.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
